make verify
pnpm exec tsc --noEmit
pnpm exec vitest run packages/web/src/plan/draftingStandards.test.ts
```

All must be green before declaring done. `make verify` runs format-check, lint, architecture, typecheck, pytest, vite build, and lockfile-check in sequence.

