git commit -m "$(cat <<'EOF'
feat(can): CAN-V3-01 plan canvas line-weight hierarchy at multiple plot scales

lineWeightsForScale() returns structured weights for 1:50/100/200/500;
projection suppressed (null) at 1:500+; grid nulls follow gridVisibilityFor;
draftingPaintFor exposes lineWeights; PlanCanvas threads suppression into
every wall/floor/roof/stair draw call; 6 new test cases in draftingStandards.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
EOF
)"
git push -u origin feat/v3-can-v3-01-line-weight-hierarchy
```

Do NOT open a PR or merge to main.

